{"tid":1720130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敎你地用RSA加密法傳重要信息","createTime":"2019-11-14T09:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:12:28.000Z","uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f060e9f2a6ae62c4c2fd66d1fab059305485f41d","tid":1720130,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp Telegram 可能有危險/用唔到<br />\n如果想用普通SMS<br />\n首先generate key pair<br />\nprivate key 唔好同第二個share<br />\nshare public key 比你朋友<br />\n你朋友用Public key 加密之後send 比你<br />\n最後你用Private key 解密<br />\n就算差佬查你message history 都鋤你唔入<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.devglan.com/online-tools/rsa-encryption-decryption\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.devglan.com%2Fonline-tools%2Frsa-encryption-decryption&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=a783b59c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.devglan.com/online-tools/rsa-encryption-decryption</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Le3W7Xx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLe3W7Xx.png&h=5e916f0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48d8a770c7e7089bab56e2d61dce354cc4c6a359","tid":1720130,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"[正視聽]點解大學據點咁重要？因為係作戰既「要塞」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2106ba8fffaebfb8a588f3768f052f35ef1c1242","tid":1720130,"uid":108285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"係就教埋人用keystore啦，或者至少收係隱藏到得你知既地方<br />\n<br />\n其實所有encryption都可以做到同樣效果，AES hash全部都得，不過好難有人咁好心機每次都轉先send姐"}]}